What is Roblox? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. It‚Äôs unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 13 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX ‚Äî interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything ‚Äî be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer ‚ÄúCapture the Flag‚Äù game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (‚ÄúRobux‚Äù). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.

snippet.title: NCTS Race at Richmond
snippet.description: The NASCAR Craftsman Truck Series regular season ends with the eero 250 at Richmond Raceway. Corey Heim picked up his sixth win of 2025 at Watkins Glen. With Stewart Friesen out for the year, Jake Garcia and Ben Rhodes are racing for a playoff spot.

snippet.title: Roblox Is Getting SUED.. (Schlep Vs. Roblox)
snippet.description:
roblox is DISGUSTING... (Schlep Roblox Lawsuit Drama EXPLAINED)

So recently Roblox Drama YouTuber Schlep known for his Pred Catching series on Roblox 'To Catch a Robloxian', where he collaborates with Ruben Sim, Jidion and more, was BANNED off of Roblox and THREATENED with a Lawsuit after Schlep received a CEASE AND DESIST from the Roblox Corporation. The Roblox Schlep Lawsuit / Ban Drama has gone VIRAL with many Large YouTuber's covering the Schlep Roblox Moderation Situation such as Charlie / MoistCritical, KreekCraft, Ruben Sim, Jidion and others. Roblox is now THREATENING to BAN other Roblox YouTubers including myself with their new HORRIBLE roblox moderation policies which Schlep had called them out for before. Since my last video Roblox RESPONDED by doubling down on their original claims and still refuse to UNBAN SCHLEP or FREE SCHLEP.

Since everything I spoke about from my last video Schlep has teamed up with Chris Hansen, and surprisingly Roblox is being sued by the general attorney of Louisiana.

Make sure to Leave a LIKE and SUBSCRIBE to help as many people as possible be made aware and informed/educated on this situation! Please watch this video to the end to be informed on the entire drama/situation!

üõ©Ô∏è  Top Gun 3 Concept 

Ever since Top Gun: Maverick reignited the franchise with critical acclaim and box office dominance, fans have been wondering: what‚Äôs next for Captain Pete ‚ÄúMaverick‚Äù Mitchell? While Paramount has yet to officially confirm a third installment, online forums, fan trailers, and speculative posts have lit the afterburners on what many are calling ‚ÄúTop Gun 3: Final Sortie.‚Äù

At the heart of the excitement is Tom Cruise, whose legendary performance as Maverick in the sequel reminded audiences why he‚Äôs one of the most enduring stars in Hollywood. While Cruise has remained tight-lipped about the potential of a third film, fan theories are already outlining a narrative where Maverick faces his most personal mission yet ‚Äî training a new international Top Gun squadron during an emerging global crisis.

Some fans suggest the film could explore the growing rivalry between manned pilots and AI-controlled fighter drones, with Maverick pushed to prove the irreplaceable value of human instinct in the cockpit. Others speculate that the story may follow Lt. Bradley ‚ÄúRooster‚Äù Bradshaw (Miles Teller), Maverick‚Äôs prot√©g√©, stepping into a leadership role ‚Äî with Cruise‚Äôs character offering mentorship in the shadows.

snippet.title: Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba Infinity Castle  |  VS TRAILER 1
snippet.description:
Tickets are on sale now for Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba Infinity Castle!

üéüÔ∏è BUY TICKETS NOW: https://www.demonslayer-movie.com/tickets/

The first feature film in the three-part cinematic trilogy arrives only in movie theatres in the United States and Canada on September 12!

Official Website: https://demonslayer-anime.com/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/demonslayer.anime/
X: https://x.com/demonslayerusa

About Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba Infinity Castle:
Tanjiro Kamado ‚Äì a boy who joined an organization dedicated to hunting down demons called the Demon Slayer Corps after his younger sister Nezuko was turned into a demon. 

While growing stronger and deepening his friendships and bonds with fellow corps members, Tanjiro has battled many demons with his comrades, Zenitsu Agatsuma and Inosuke Hashibira. Along the way, his journey has led him to fight alongside the Demon Slayer Corps‚Äô highest-ranking swordsmen, the Hashira, including Flame Hashira Kyojuro Rengoku aboard the Mugen Train, Sound Hashira Tengen Uzui within the Entertainment District, as well as Mist Hashira Muichiro Tokito and Love Hashira Mitsuri Kanroji at the Swordsmith Village.

As the Demon Slayer Corps members and Hashira engaged in a group strength training program, the Hashira Training, in preparation for the forthcoming battle against the demons, Muzan Kibutsuji appears at the Ubuyashiki Mansion. With the head of the Demon Corps in danger, Tanjiro and the Hashira rush to the headquarters but are plunged into a deep descent to a mysterious space by the hands of Muzan Kibutsuji.
The destination of where Tanjiro and Demon Slayer Corps have fallen is the demons‚Äô stronghold ‚Äì the Infinity Castle. 

And so, the battleground is set as the final battle between the Demon Slayer Corps and the demons ignites.

[ STAFF ]
Original Story: Koyoharu Gotoge (JUMP COMICS / SHUEISHA)
Director: Haruo Sotozaki
Character Design/Chief Animation Director: Akira Matsushima
Screenplay: ufotable 
Sub Character Design: Miyuki Sato, Yoko Kajiyama, Mika Kikuchi
Prop Design: Masaharu Koyama
Art Director: Koji Eto
Director of Photography/Creative Finishing Work Director: Yuichi Terao
3D Director: Kazuki Nishiwaki
Color Setting: Yuko Omae
Editing: Manabu Kamino
Music: Go Shiina, Yuki Kajiura
Chief Director: Hikaru Kondo
Animation Production: ufotable

Theme Songs: 
"A World Where the Sun Never Rises" by Aimer (SACRA MUSIC / Sony Music Labels Inc.) 
"Shine in the Cruel Night" by LiSA (SACRA MUSIC / Sony Music Labels Inc.)

[ CAST ]

Nezuko Kamado: Akari Kito
Zenitsu Agatsuma: Hiro Shimono
Inosuke Hashibira: Yoshitsugu Matsuoka
Kanao Tsuyuri: Reina Ueda

id.title: Teaser Hari Baru Spider-Man: Spider-Man vs Punisher & Hulk
id.description:
Trailer Teaser Spider-Man Brand New Day 2026. Spider-Man vs Punisher Jon Bernthal, Mark Ruffalo Hulk, Spider-Man vs Scorpion, Penjelasan Adegan Pertempuran Punisher di Van, Reuni Jon Bernthal dengan Tom Holland & Sony Marvel Trailer Spider-Man Brand New Day ‚ñ∫ https://bit.ly/AwesomeSubscribe
Trailer Spider-Man Brand New Day https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=B_59lBNjosE&list=PLOIeYdZ3QczxQXxyV_2D8kuEs_QsuQIyJ&index=1&pp=gAQBiAQB

Es Krim Superman & Referensi https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QgoyaMHk2RQ&list=PLOIeYdZ3QczwCLH9RIm-7ui56ameRYmdQ&index=2&pp=gAQBiAQB0gcJCdgJAYcqIYzv
Adegan Pasca-Kredit Superman https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7NVbJdIHKTA&list=PLOIeYdZ3QczwCLH9RIm-7ui56ameRYmdQ&index=1&pp=gAQBiAQB
Tampilan Perdana Avengers: Kiamat https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2E1gEtPrzj0&list=PLOIeYdZ3QczwWT3yd94Xc6n-ooI85uV_u&index=1&pp=gAQBiAQB
Trailer Avengers: Kiamat https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bQfK5VSwLHQ&list=PLOIeYdZ3QczwWT3yd94Xc6n-ooI85uV_u&index=1&pp=gAQBiAQB
Video Terbaru Keren https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FeOfhzu7ZdY&list=PLOIeYdZ3QczxQXxyV_2D8kuEs_QsuQIyJ&index=7

Meliputi Cuplikan Hari Baru Spider-Man, Spider-Man vs Punisher, Penjelasan Van Pertempuran Punisher. Reuni Tom Holland dan Jon Bernthal. Tampilan Pertama Kostum Spider-Man Baru. Pengumuman Hulk. Mengapa Bruce Banner akan membantu Spider-Man, Spider-Man vs Hulk, referensi sebelumnya tentang Hulk dalam Film Spider-Man. Stan Lee, Incredible Hulk dan Spider-Man Live Action Crossover di tahun 1980-an. Scorpion Returns, Tombstone, dan penjahat baru lainnya.

Penjelasan Spider-Man Brand New Day. Penjahat Baru, Perubahan Tom Holland di Spider-Man, Koneksi Trailer Avengers Doomsday. Karakter Baru, Kostum Spider-Man Baru. Trailer Spider-Man Beyond The Spider-Verse. Trailer Spider-Man Noir, Koneksi Sadie Sink dengan Tobey Maguire di Spider-Man.

Trailer Avengers Doomsday. Robert Downey Jr. Doctor Doom, Black Panther Baru, X-Men, Doctor Strange, Tampilan Pertama Avengers Secret Wars, Battleworld MCU. Fantastic Four, Franklin Richards. Ian McKellen Magneto, Patrick Stewart Professor X, Kesley Grammer Beast, Thor Returns, Mystique, Cyclops, Nightcrawler, X-Men Asli.

Easter Egg Deadpool dan Wolverine. Lelucon Marvel Kevin Feige dan Runtuhnya Tembok Keempat. Lelucon Adegan Pasca Kredit Deadpool dan Wolverine. Mengapa Deadpool Menyelamatkan Wolverine, X-Men, Fantastic Four, dan Deadpool Menyelamatkan MCU. Bagaimana Deadpool dan Wolverine mempersiapkan Avengers 6 Secret Wars dengan Battleworld dan Loki Musim 2 Berakhir dengan Easter Egg Crossover God Loki

Mengapa Marvel me-reboot MCU dengan Avengers 6 Secret Wars? Apa yang akan berubah dengan semua Avengers, New Iron Man, X-Men Mutants seperti Wolverine, Deadpool, Fantastic Four, Ghost Rider, Spider-Man, dan karakter lainnya.

Banyak Trailer Marvel lainnya akan hadir, Trailer Avengers Doomsday, Lebih banyak video Spider-Man Brand New Day akan segera hadir, video Fantastic Four & Superman!

snippet.title: Exposing Roblox‚Äôs Predator Protection Pattern‚Ä¶
snippet.description:
Roblox just banned Schlep... and I think I know the answer.

Schlep is a Roblox Youtuber that catches and gets Roblox predators arrested. But Roblox has banned and threatened to sue Schlep. On top of that, Roblox recently released a statement condemning all ‚Äúvigilante activities‚Äù. With this sort of response, why is Roblox being so aggressive?

Well it‚Äôs part of a pattern. A pattern where Roblox (like me) hides from its problems.

And this Schlep ban is only one of the multiple different instances where Roblox exacerbates its predator problem for the sake of shareholder value. There‚Äôs Roblox UGC emotes being a horrible idea, yet it‚Äôs still being added. There‚Äôs Roblox‚Äôs open source sentinel AI, when Roblox‚Äôs AI moderation is as blind as Helen Keller. And there‚Äôs Roblox‚Äôs plan to add dating, on a platform with a predator problem‚Ä¶

This isn‚Äôt about the kids, it‚Äôs about the kash (horrible pun I apologize) Also I finished this at like 1:30 am which is 5.5 hours before this video goes live so like I hope you like it. If you don't like it, tuff.

snippet.title: 100 Players Simulate Minecraft's Deadliest Hunger Games!
snippet.description:
100 Players Simulate Minecraft's Deadliest Hunger Games!
-------------------------------------------------------------

Join my Discord for FUTURE EVENTS - https://discord.gg/sword4000

-------------------------------------------------------------

üì∑ Follow my Instagram ‚ñ∫ https://www.instagram.com/sword4000_/
üé¨ Edited By @SwordExtra @ccleaf 

All Animations by - https://store.ccleaf.com/

In this event, I invited 100 of the highest ranked content creators, pvpers, trappers and builders to the 3rd Annual Hunger Games, and place them in an arena for 5 days with the goal to be the last player standing. After months of practice, and years of preparation, will I be able to take down the best players in the world and win the hunger games? Let's find out!

snippet.title: Lorna Shore - Prison Of Flesh (Official Video)
snippet.description:
Lorna Shore - Prison Of Flesh - Official Video. From the new album 'I Feel The Everblack Festering Within Me' - September 12 2025. Get it now: 
https://ifeeltheeverblackfesteringwithinme.com/
https://lornashoreband.com/
https://linktr.ee/IFTEFWM

ON TOUR W/
THE BLACK DAHLIA MURDER
SHADOW OF INTENT 
PEELINGFLESH
TICKETS: https://lornashoreband.com/pages/tour

"This song is exactly what I imagine a lot of people expected of us to put out. We took all the heaviest stuff we had, to create this incredibly dark, high-stress/tension song. I personally think the breakdown at the end of this is one of my favorites that we‚Äôve ever written and I‚Äôm excited to see how people engage with this one.

The lyrics for this song are about my family and our history of dementia. The idea that the world is falling apart, and about the fear of losing touch with reality. ‚ÄúThey‚Äôre coming to get me‚Äù is my way of personifying ‚Äòdemons‚Äô or something that makes you feel like you‚Äôre losing pieces of yourself. The closer they get, the further detached you become until you‚Äôre nothing but a husk of fear and delusion." - WILL RAMOS

LYRICS //

I CAN‚ÄôT TELL WHERE TO GO
I‚ÄôM FALLING UNTO TWILIGHT
WHERE THE SHADOWS MEET MY SKIN
SOMETHING HAS COME FOR MY MIND
SLOWLY IT EATS ME INSIDE
AND I CAN FEEL
THEY‚ÄôRE COMING TO GET ME
I FEEL IT CLOSING IN
THEY‚ÄôRE COMING TO GET ME
WHERE DO I GO FROM HERE NOW 
I FEEL THEIR GRIP
CLOSING IN ON MY WILTING SOUL
RIPPING APART ALL THE ROOTS THAT HELD ME IN CONTROL
MAKE ME WHOLE, OR SPLIT ME IN TWO  
DESENSITIZE MY SORROW
REPLACE MY INSIDES
A HOLLOW BODY VACANT OF ALL BUT FEAR
I CAN‚ÄôT ESCAPE THE DARK WITHIN
THESE DEMONS RESIDE IN ME

I AM FADING, FASTER
SEARCHING FOR ANSWERS IN THE DARK UNTIL I DEPART
I DRANK FROM THE RIVER
WITHERED, LOST IN THE VOID OF MY MIND
I‚ÄôVE COME TO FIND
I‚ÄôM RUNNING OUT OF TIME
THEY‚ÄôRE COMING TO GET ME
FOREVER LOST IN THE DARK
I‚ÄôM RUNNING FOR MY LIFE
LOSING PIECES OF WHAT IS LEFT OF MY SANITY
I, EVIDENTLY, AM BECOMING EMPTY INSIDE OF THIS SHELL
WHAT‚ÄôVE I BECOME
WHERE DO I GO FROM HERE
NOW I FEEL THEIR GRIP
BREAKING ME DOWN
GRASPING AT MY NECK 
PLAYING WITH MEMORIES 
ALL I AM IS FUCKING SICK
I CANNOT BREATHE INSIDE THIS HELL
SUFFOCATE ALL REASON
I AM NOTHING BUT BARREN
A PRISON OF FLESH TO CONFINE THE CURSE WITHIN MY BROOD
I CAN‚ÄôT ESCAPE THE DARK WITHIN
THESE DEMONS RESIDE IN ME

I AM FADING, FASTER
SEARCHING FOR ANSWERS IN THE DARK UNTIL I DEPART
I DRANK FROM THE RIVER
WITHERED, LOST IN THE VOID OF MY MIND
I‚ÄôVE COME TO FIND
I‚ÄôM RUNNING OUT OF TIME
THEY‚ÄôRE COMING TO GET ME
COMING BACK FOR ME
BURN AWAY THE HATE
I WILL SUFFOCATE IN THE ASHEN WAKE
COMING BACK FOR ME
BURN AWAY THE HATE
I WILL SUFFOCATE
 
I DESCEND INTO THE VOID OF EVER GROWING NIGHT
WHEN I‚ÄôM FALLING IN YOU PULL ME BACK
I FEEL THE EVER BLACK
FESTERING WITHIN ME
THEY‚ÄôRE COMING TO GET ME

snippet.title: Past Life #6 - Boogeyman Loyalty Test
snippet.description:
Past Life is an odd mix of a Social and PvP Minecraft game started by Grian. Players are thrown into a tiny world with almost no rules, except survive as long as possible.

In Past Life, we will be playing through the older versions of Minecraft and updating to a newer one each episode.

3+ Lives = Green Player
2 Lives = Yellow Player
1 Life = Red Player

Red Players are given the goal of killing all the other players in the game. Yellow Players can kill Green Players.

snippet.title: Unofficial Skyrim Patch | Down the Rabbit Hole
snippet.description:
When a group of modders band together to create the ultimate bug fixing patch for Skyrim, the popularity of the project draws scrutiny and backlash that only grows as time passes.

EXTRA INFORMATION:

At 10:36, the mod shows the incorrect attribution. It should read "Acquisitive Soul Gems mod and screenshot by bluedanieru"

Also, a clarification: at about 30 minutes, it is mentioned that the post was made in 2014 but the date on the post shown is 2017. This is because the shown image is of a repost of the original 2014 post.



Soundtrack by Ryan Probert available here: https://youtu.be/OMZ9QUX35ac

Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/c/fredrikknudsen



The Patch is Announced: 0:00

The First Controversy: 4:29

Disagreements over Definition: 18:43

Arthmoor is Finally Banned: 38:49

Wabbajack: 52:56

Blame Improperly Assigned: 1:01:49

The Community Revolts: 1:11:48

The Unofficial Patch Survives: 1:22:05

snippet.title: Gavin Adcock - Last One To Know (Official Music Video)
snippet.description:
Gavin Adcock - Last One To Know (Official Music Video)

TOUR DATES: https://www.gavinadcockmusic.com/tour

FOLLOW:
Official Website: https://www.gavinadcockmusic.com
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/gavinadcockmusic
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@gavinadcockmusic 
X: https://twitter.com/gavinadcock

Gavin Adcock is a Georgia native born and raised in Watkinsville. Former Georgia
Southern University football player, Gavin grew up working on his family cattle farm and
dreamed of riding bulls in the PBR. He started writing songs in high school, but it wasn‚Äôt
until the spring of 2021, when Adcock tore his knee playing football, that he used his
healing time to record and release his first original single. Since then, Gavin has
released multiple singles, collectively amassing over 1 billion global streams including
the fan-favorite, RIAA PLATINUM-certified, ‚ÄúA Cigarette,‚Äù GOLD-certified songs ‚ÄúRun
Your Mouth,‚Äù ‚ÄúDeep End,‚Äù and ‚ÄúFour Leaf Clover,‚Äù along with his major label debut
album, Actin‚Äô Up Again, which was crowned the largest major-label country debut from a
solo male artist released in 2024. With more than 15 million on-demand U.S. streams
week of release, Actin‚Äô Up Again was also 2024‚Äôs top streaming major-label debut
across the whole genre. One year after his thunderous album Actin‚Äô Up Again released
worldwide, Adcock is set to release his next album, Own Worst Enemy, on August 15,
2025. Throughout the meteoric year from Actin‚Äô Up Again (2024) to Own Worst Enemy
(2025), the Georgia native has won over the hearts of both Country music fans and the
Country music industry alike. Adcock received his first industry voted award nomination
for New Male Artist of the Year for the 60 th ACM Awards, in addition to being nominated
for MusicRow Magazine‚Äôs ‚ÄúDISCOVERY ARTIST OF THE YEAR‚Äù award for the 37 th
Annual MusicRow Awards. Taking his music to the fans, Adcock has sold out music
venues from coast-to-coast via multiple headline tours such as the Monster Energy
Outbreak Tour Presents: Gavin Adcock, his Actin‚Äô Up Again (Again) Tour, and at
present his Need To Tour, which kicked off in May 2025. Adcock also joins superstar
Morgan Wallen for select dates on Wallen‚Äôs I‚Äôm The Problem Tour, as well as a plethora
of new headline dates and major festival appearances being added throughout the rest
of 2025.

#GavinAdcock #LastOneToKnow #OwnWorstEnemy

Tags:
What is Roblox? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. It‚Äôs unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 8 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX ‚Äî interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything ‚Äî be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer ‚ÄúCapture the Flag‚Äù game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (‚ÄúRobux‚Äù). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.

snippet.title: Playing Every Huff N‚Äô Puff That Exists!
snippet.description:
We are BACK at the Casino playing EVERY SINGLE Huff N‚Äô Puff Slot Machine that has ever been made.  Let‚Äôs see which ones are winners, and which ones are MUSH.  Thank you all so much for liking, subscribing, and dropping your thoughts in the comments. Even if you‚Äôre roasting me‚ÄîI still love you. You‚Äôre all beautiful, and I truly appreciate every single one of you for riding along on this crazy journey.  Wish me luck, and I‚Äôll see you in the next one! Let‚Äôs go to war.

Ôøº Brettski adjusted his lucky flamingo shirt and strode into the glowing belly of Silver Mirage Casino, a man on a singular mission: to play every *Huff N‚Äô Puff* slot machine under the roof. Rumor had it, one machine‚Äîonly one‚Äîheld a progressive jackpot that hadn‚Äôt hit in seven years. Brettski, a slot whisperer in certain circles, intended to sniff it out.

The first machine was cold. The second teased him with three hard hats, then nothing. By the fifth machine, Brettski was down \$342 and beginning to question if the myth was just that. But on machine six‚ÄîBAM‚Äîbonus round. Pigs flew, huffed, puffed, and he walked away up \$1,200. "Just getting warm," he muttered.

Then came machine twelve.

It wasn't on the map. Hidden in a back hallway near the employees-only door, flickering like it hadn‚Äôt been touched since the Clinton administration. Brettski felt it immediately. The hum. The tension. The way the reels clicked when he sat down‚Äîlike they recognized him.

He inserted a crisp hundred.

First spin: bonus. Second spin: RE-TRIGGER. The screen exploded with gold hats. The Big Bad Wolf practically winked at him. The machine roared to life, sucking in lights from the floor, as if awakening. People gathered.

The jackpot ticker climbed: \$112,000‚Ä¶ \$240,000‚Ä¶ then froze at **\$777,777.77**.

A voice blared from above: **‚ÄúPayout locked. Identity verification required.‚Äù**

Security swarmed. The crowd backed up. Brettski stood, bewildered, as two men in black suits emerged from the side door.

‚ÄúMr. Brettski,‚Äù one said, ‚Äúyou weren‚Äôt supposed to find this machine.‚Äù

The other held a briefcase. ‚ÄúYou‚Äôve activated Protocol Seven.‚Äù

‚ÄúWhat the hell is Protocol Seven?‚Äù Brettski asked, but before they could answer‚Äî

The lights cut out.

The machine restarted itself.

And the seat was suddenly‚Ä¶ empty.

nl-NL.title: Ik speel elke Huff N‚Äô Puff die er bestaat!
nl-NL.description:
We zijn TERUG in het casino en spelen ELKE Huff N‚Äô Puff gokkast die ooit gemaakt is. Laten we eens kijken welke winnend zijn en welke MUSH. Heel erg bedankt allemaal voor het liken, abonneren en het achterlaten van jullie mening in de reacties. Zelfs als jullie me belachelijk maken ‚Äì ik hou nog steeds van jullie. Jullie zijn allemaal prachtig, en ik waardeer het enorm dat jullie allemaal mee hebben gedaan aan deze waanzinnige reis. Wens me succes en ik zie jullie bij de volgende! Laten we ten strijde trekken.

Ôøº Brettski trok zijn geluksflamingoshirt recht en stapte de gloeiende buik van Silver Mirage Casino binnen, een man met een unieke missie: elke *Huff N‚Äô Puff* gokkast onder het dak spelen. Het gerucht ging dat √©√©n machine ‚Äì maar √©√©n ‚Äì een progressieve jackpot had die al zeven jaar niet was gevallen. Brettski, een gokkastfluisteraar in bepaalde kringen, was van plan om die te ontdekken.

De eerste machine was koud. De tweede plaagde hem met drie helmen, en toen niets. Bij de vijfde machine was Brettski $342 kwijt en begon hij zich af te vragen of de mythe alleen maar dat was. Maar op machine zes ‚Äì BAM ‚Äì bonusronde. Varkens vlogen, hijgden, puften, en hij liep $1200 omhoog. "Ik word net warm," mompelde hij.

Toen kwam machine twaalf.

Die stond niet op de kaart. Verstopt in een achtergang bij de deur, alleen voor werknemers, flikkerend alsof hij sinds de regering-Clinton niet meer was aangeraakt. Brettski voelde het meteen. Het gezoem. De spanning. De manier waarop de rollen klikten toen hij ging zitten ‚Äì alsof ze hem herkenden.

Hij gooide een scherpe honderd in.

Eerste draai: bonus. Tweede draai: RE-TRIGGER. Het scherm explodeerde met gouden hoeden. De Grote Boze Wolf knipoogde bijna naar hem. De machine kwam brullend tot leven en zoog licht op van de vloer, alsof hij ontwaakte. Mensen verzamelden zich.

De jackpot-ticker klom omhoog: $112.000‚Ä¶ $240.000‚Ä¶ en bleef toen stilstaan op **$777.777,77**.

Een stem klonk van boven: **"Uitbetaling geblokkeerd. Identiteitsverificatie vereist."**

De beveiliging dromde samen. De menigte deinsde achteruit. Brettski stond verbijsterd op toen twee mannen in zwarte pakken uit de zijdeur tevoorschijn kwamen.

"Meneer Brettski," zei de een, "u had deze machine niet mogen vinden."

De ander hield een aktetas vast. "U hebt Protocol Zeven geactiveerd."

"Wat is Protocol Zeven in vredesnaam?" vroeg Brettski, maar voordat ze konden antwoorden‚Äî

De lichten vielen uit.

De machine startte zichzelf opnieuw op.

En de stoel was plotseling... leeg.

snippet.title: The Unstable SMP Experience
snippet.description:
The Unstable SMP is the Biggest Hardcore Minecraft Server in the world, with tens of thousands of players online at any given moment. However, on Unstable, you only have one life. If you die, you're permanently banned. This is The Unstable SMP Experience. 

Like ParrotX2 and his Unstable SMP series, where he is escaping Paragon / Proton: Minecraft's Most Secure Prison, or got hunted by a Minecraft Player who doesn't exist. This is a new and original Minecraft idea like HermitCraft or Lifesteal with Wemmbu, FlameFrags, or Spoke. Survival is harder than Hardcore Minecraft because PVP is on.

People in this video: @TheobaldTheBird @reddoons @Boosfer PuqiTV @FlameFragsMC @dragon_mc_ @fymada @lezywezy @creakyv @finlooooo @RecallingMan @Hexatope @CaveUnderscore @qCxsh @nezoshoki @TheSorta1 

This is Episode 7 of Season 2 Parrot Videos on the Unstable SMP :)

This is a video on the Unstable Universe: a staged Minecraft server where ParrotX2, Wemmbu, Spoke, and FlameFrags tell stories in Minecraft.

A Minecraft video made by Parrot or ParrotX2 on other platforms! Enjoy!
